si_remarks: An experiment with a reference and a thinned plot. Located about 450 m SSE of the Norunda flux tower (http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/S0168-1923(99)00092-1). Similar type of forest but younger compared to the main footprint of the tower, which is about 100 years.
